        <abstract> 
<p>CD is collecting [for <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] all accounts of what some call "sports" and what he calls "bud-variations". He asks whether very slight variations in fruit appear suddenly by buds, or whether only rather strongly marked varieties thus appear.</p> 
